1
00:00:24,030 --> 00:00:25,290
[[Adapted from a novel published on
Qidian Reading under China Literature]]

2
00:00:25,320 --> 00:00:27,180
["Way of Choices" by Mao Ni]

3
00:00:28,300 --> 00:00:29,830
[Minors]

4
00:00:29,860 --> 00:00:31,550
[should watch with guardian consent]

5
00:02:14,740 --> 00:02:19,370
[Way of Choices]

6
00:02:21,230 --> 00:02:24,690
[Previously]

7
00:02:21,720 --> 00:02:23,160
To win the Imperial Court Exam,

8
00:02:23,160 --> 00:02:25,220
I have to reach Seated Illumination.

9
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:27,160
You're not afraid of death?

10
00:02:27,640 --> 00:02:28,700
I do not wish to die.

11
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:30,840
Yet a promise is a matter of great import.

12
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:32,200
I'll teach you dragon language.

13
00:02:32,200 --> 00:02:34,000
You help me break the formation.

14
00:02:35,750 --> 00:02:36,350
Watch out.

15
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:38,280
The formation has changed.

16
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:41,210
The evil dragon has broken free
without permission.

17
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:43,240
It deserves death.

18
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:46,000
I never had a choice from the start.

19
00:02:46,480 --> 00:02:47,740
Seated Illumination.

20
00:02:48,079 --> 00:02:49,040
Burning Star.

21
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:51,480
Chen Changsheng,

22
00:02:52,480 --> 00:02:53,370
are you

23
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,800
my destiny?

24
00:02:55,079 --> 00:02:57,040
Or am I yours?

25
00:02:57,890 --> 00:02:59,950
Looks like this land of certain death

26
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:01,990
is your land of blessing.

27
00:03:02,640 --> 00:03:03,400
Master,

28
00:03:03,920 --> 00:03:04,750
Senior,

29
00:03:05,320 --> 00:03:06,720
the day has finally come.

30
00:03:12,020 --> 00:03:13,270
[Hall of Light]

31
00:03:42,079 --> 00:03:42,960
They're coming.

32
00:03:42,220 --> 00:03:42,930
[Sacrificial Fire Academy]

33
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:44,520
All academies from every kingdom are here.

34
00:03:43,010 --> 00:03:44,420
[Li Palace Affiliate]

35
00:03:44,420 --> 00:03:45,370
[Tiandao Academy]

36
00:03:45,370 --> 00:03:46,050
[Zhaixing Academy]

37
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:46,920
Come on, Tiandao Academy!

38
00:03:46,050 --> 00:03:46,690
[Saintess Peak]

39
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:49,770
We can't let Southern Realms
win again this year.

40
00:03:57,190 --> 00:03:59,650
[Saintess Peak] [Zhaixing Academy]
[Li Palace Affiliate]

41
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:13,570
Master,

42
00:04:13,920 --> 00:04:14,760
Senior,

43
00:04:14,890 --> 00:04:16,350
this day has finally come.

44
00:04:17,970 --> 00:04:19,329
The welcome ceremony

45
00:04:19,440 --> 00:04:20,279
is not bad.

46
00:04:20,279 --> 00:04:21,880
He isn’t even on the Blue Cloud List,

47
00:04:21,880 --> 00:04:23,080
yet he dares to claim
he’ll take first place.

48
00:04:23,080 --> 00:04:24,040
What nerve.

49
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:26,160
I heard the grandson of the Tang family
of Wenshui has lost his mind,

50
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,720
betting everything on him.

51
00:04:28,840 --> 00:04:30,520
Arrogant fool.

52
00:04:31,320 --> 00:04:33,920
How dare he announce that he’ll win?

53
00:04:31,580 --> 00:04:35,090
[Initial Stage of Sitting Enlightenment,
Zhong Hui]

54
00:04:34,159 --> 00:04:36,159
Are you insulting our Huai Academy?

55
00:04:36,320 --> 00:04:37,320
Chen Changsheng!

56
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,040
You...

57
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:39,230
How dare you?

58
00:04:43,159 --> 00:04:45,760
How dare you look down on us
from the Southern Realms?

59
00:04:44,490 --> 00:04:46,090
[Initial Stage of Sitting Enlightenment, Ling Fei]
[Initial Stage of Sitting Enlightenment, Liu Chongshan]

60
00:04:46,200 --> 00:04:47,360
You want to die?

61
00:04:47,520 --> 00:04:48,240
What?

62
00:04:48,320 --> 00:04:49,710
You don't even have the True Essence?

63
00:04:49,710 --> 00:04:50,950
[Initial Stage of Sitting Enlightenment,
Huo Guang]

64
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,320
What if I accidentally

65
00:04:51,320 --> 00:04:53,080
kill you with one punch?

66
00:04:57,760 --> 00:04:58,420
Silly bear,

67
00:04:58,560 --> 00:04:59,760
why did you eat so much?

68
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:01,440
I heard the Imperial Court Exam
will take a long time.

69
00:05:01,440 --> 00:05:02,600
I need to be full.

70
00:05:03,400 --> 00:05:04,280
That makes sense.

71
00:05:04,280 --> 00:05:05,410
Unlike some people,

72
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:06,600
who don’t eat enough

73
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:08,060
but talk way too much crap.

74
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:12,880
Zhong Hui,

75
00:05:14,200 --> 00:05:16,130
we represent the Southern Realms.

76
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:17,360
Don’t disgrace us with bad manners

77
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,560
inside the Li Palace.

78
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:24,440
We agreed to fight.

79
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:25,920
Don’t stand me up.

80
00:05:26,640 --> 00:05:27,100
I won’t.

81
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:30,720
I hope your bones

82
00:05:30,840 --> 00:05:32,370
are harder than your mouth.

83
00:05:44,520 --> 00:05:46,880
Grand Pontiff is here!

84
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:58,120
Grand Pontiff destroyed
the State Religious Academy,

85
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,510
yet he let you enroll.

86
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:01,960
Now he’s testing you
in the Imperial Court Exam.

87
00:06:01,960 --> 00:06:03,420
What exactly does he want?

88
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:04,850
I don't know.

89
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:06,880
But no matter what he's thinking,

90
00:06:06,880 --> 00:06:07,800
I must win.

91
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:11,100
Greetings to Grand Pontiff.

92
00:06:11,280 --> 00:06:14,000
May the starlight be with you eternally.

93
00:06:17,540 --> 00:06:21,070
Since the Grand Ancestor established
the Imperial Court Exam,

94
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:24,920
countless mighty masters
have been selected.

95
00:06:25,320 --> 00:06:28,920
Their names are carved
at the top of the Continent.

96
00:06:27,700 --> 00:06:31,100
[Zhong Liyue, Lu Yuan, Zhou Wangren]

97
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:30,720
and beneath the starry sky.

98
00:06:31,400 --> 00:06:32,840
Yet these names

99
00:06:32,840 --> 00:06:35,560
are not for the world to worship.

100
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:37,480
They are here to inspire all of you

101
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:39,480
to surpass them.

102
00:06:39,640 --> 00:06:40,280
This

103
00:06:40,280 --> 00:06:43,000
is the meaning of the Imperial Court Exam.

104
00:06:43,520 --> 00:06:45,520
This year's Imperial Court Exam

105
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:50,640
will take place
in Grand Pontiff's Green Leaf World.

106
00:06:50,640 --> 00:06:52,520
There are three rounds in total.

107
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:54,640
The first round is Literary Test.

108
00:06:52,860 --> 00:06:54,430
[Tongwen Hall]

109
00:06:54,840 --> 00:06:56,850
Those with excellent scores

110
00:06:56,960 --> 00:06:59,000
will advance to the second round,

111
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,840
Divine Consciousness Maze.

112
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,840
Those who exit the maze

113
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:04,780
within two hours

114
00:07:04,840 --> 00:07:07,560
will advance to the third round:
Martial Test.

115
00:07:07,630 --> 00:07:12,830
[Li Palace Affiliate]

116
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:10,640
The final ranking will be determined

117
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:12,920
by the total scores of all three rounds.

118
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:14,840
The top three will enter

119
00:07:14,960 --> 00:07:19,080
the Heavenly Book Mausoleum
for the Monuments.

120
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:21,160
The champion of this exam

121
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:23,400
will be granted entry
to the Lingyan Pavilion

122
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:26,240
to witness the inheritance of the sages.

123
00:07:28,960 --> 00:07:30,320
The way to change one's fate

124
00:07:30,320 --> 00:07:31,960
lies within Lingyan Pavilion.

125
00:07:31,960 --> 00:07:33,670
Only by being the top scorer

126
00:07:33,840 --> 00:07:35,110
can you see it.

127
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:39,720
The auspicious time has come.

128
00:07:39,840 --> 00:07:41,440
Imperial Court Exam

129
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:43,560
begins!

130
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:53,040
So this is
the Grand Pontiff's small world.

131
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:54,800
They say a single leaf holds a world.

132
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:56,360
Truly the power of a sage.

133
00:08:10,630 --> 00:08:13,010
[Imperial Court Exam: Literary Test]

134
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:24,300
I'm Mo Jiu,
the host of the Imperial Court Exam.

135
00:08:24,400 --> 00:08:25,240
Next,

136
00:08:25,260 --> 00:08:27,660
let me explain the rules for the test.

137
00:08:28,400 --> 00:08:29,480
This literary test consists

138
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:30,760
of 36 papers.

139
00:08:30,760 --> 00:08:32,200
The more papers you finish,

140
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:33,460
the higher your score.

141
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,280
Once you complete your answers,

142
00:08:35,280 --> 00:08:37,940
the Tongwen Beasts
on your left will grade them.

143
00:08:38,520 --> 00:08:39,159
Everyone,

144
00:08:39,640 --> 00:08:41,159
it is now 9 AM.

145
00:08:44,159 --> 00:08:44,920
This is...

146
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,900
[Special Merit: Demon Slaying]

147
00:08:46,800 --> 00:08:47,640
Amazing.

148
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:48,680
You...

149
00:08:48,680 --> 00:08:49,410
have passed.

150
00:08:50,160 --> 00:08:51,820
Why is he exempt from the test?

151
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:53,800
A first-class merit medallion.

152
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:55,440
Legend says only those
who earned supreme merit

153
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:56,800
on the Demon Race battlefield

154
00:08:56,800 --> 00:08:58,130
can receive such honor.

155
00:08:58,400 --> 00:08:59,730
The Imperial Court Exam

156
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:01,200
is truly full of hidden talents.

157
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:02,240
All examinees,

158
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:04,160
the literary test begins!

159
00:09:26,760 --> 00:09:28,200
Time's up.

160
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:30,200
Pens down, everyone.

161
00:09:30,280 --> 00:09:31,320
Begin grading.

162
00:09:34,800 --> 00:09:36,080
Shallow knowledge,

163
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:37,040
and full of flaws.

164
00:09:37,040 --> 00:09:37,600
Out.

165
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:39,240
Riddled with mistakes.

166
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:39,920
Out.

167
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:41,560
Chaotic reasoning.

168
00:09:41,560 --> 00:09:42,200
Out.

169
00:09:42,280 --> 00:09:43,360
Shallow perspective.

170
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:44,160
Out.

171
00:09:45,680 --> 00:09:47,120
Elegant writing.

172
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,020
Excellent.

173
00:09:48,400 --> 00:09:49,960
Profound artistic conception.

174
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:50,620
Excellent.

175
00:09:51,280 --> 00:09:53,960
Simple yet powerful expression.

176
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:56,000
[Simple and Powerful]

177
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:56,120
Not bad.

178
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:59,000
Examinees Chen Changsheng

179
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:00,040
and Gou Hanshi

180
00:10:00,040 --> 00:10:01,960
have completed all 36 papers.

181
00:10:02,040 --> 00:10:03,200
Flawless answers,

182
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:04,680
exquisite beyond compare.

183
00:10:04,680 --> 00:10:05,680
Rating:

184
00:10:05,760 --> 00:10:07,000
Exceptional.

185
00:10:06,180 --> 00:10:09,670
[Chen Changsheng] [Gou Hanshi]

186
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:09,560
They are tied as the top of the test.

187
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:16,360
Great.

188
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:17,560
You've advanced.

189
00:10:17,560 --> 00:10:18,920
Now the real fun begins.

190
00:10:20,640 --> 00:10:23,040
Chen Changsheng does have some talent.

191
00:10:23,280 --> 00:10:25,480
No wonder Yourong favors him.

192
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:26,840
No matter how good he is
at literary tests,

193
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:28,600
it's only skill on paper.

194
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:30,960
The next two rounds are what truly matter.

195
00:10:31,280 --> 00:10:33,400
Second Round of the Imperial Court Exam:

196
00:10:31,460 --> 00:10:33,690
[Imperial Court Exam:
Divine Consciousness Maze]

197
00:10:33,400 --> 00:10:35,000
Divine Consciousness Maze.

198
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:37,440
You must exit the maze within two hours

199
00:10:37,520 --> 00:10:40,040
and reach Xichen Tower,
the site of the martial test.

200
00:10:39,930 --> 00:10:41,370
[Xichen Tower]

201
00:10:40,040 --> 00:10:41,570
Only then will you advance.

202
00:10:41,940 --> 00:10:45,000
Forty percent of candidates were
eliminated in the first round.

203
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:46,640
Only 120 people remain.

204
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:48,800
How many will fall in this second round,

205
00:10:48,800 --> 00:10:50,600
the Divine Consciousness Maze?

206
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:51,920
The maze has complex terrain.

207
00:10:51,920 --> 00:10:53,080
The stronger your divine consciousness,

208
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:54,610
the wider your perception,

209
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:57,080
and the faster you can find the exit.

210
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:01,320
The exit is...

211
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:02,160
that way.

212
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:19,380
If I recall correctly,

213
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:21,080
this isn't the martial test.

214
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:22,080
Blame yourself

215
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:24,520
for making everyone angry.

216
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:31,400
That's the signal.

217
00:11:31,400 --> 00:11:31,840
Let's go!

218
00:11:31,840 --> 00:11:33,770
Teach that arrogant brat a lesson.

219
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:36,800
Using force in the maze

220
00:11:36,800 --> 00:11:38,080
has no precedent.

221
00:11:38,160 --> 00:11:40,450
But it’s not forbidden either.

222
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:42,360
He brought this on himself.

223
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:45,160
With all this resentment building up,

224
00:11:45,160 --> 00:11:47,640
it’s about to explode.

225
00:11:49,640 --> 00:11:50,560
Director Chen,

226
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:52,320
I’ve bet everything I have on you.

227
00:11:52,320 --> 00:11:53,410
If you lose,

228
00:11:53,680 --> 00:11:55,720
you’ll have to fish me out of the river!

229
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:57,160
Breaking news.

230
00:11:57,280 --> 00:11:59,760
Chen Changsheng is being attacked
by other candidates.

231
00:11:59,760 --> 00:12:00,490
Oh no!

232
00:12:00,520 --> 00:12:02,080
I just bet a huge sum on him.

233
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:04,080
Then you’re gonna lose everything.

234
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:06,400
Make way.

235
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:08,000
Young Master said

236
00:12:08,160 --> 00:12:09,360
The Tang family of Wenshui

237
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:12,220
still bets on Chen
and the State Religious Academy.

238
00:12:12,280 --> 00:12:13,120
Dare you take

239
00:12:13,360 --> 00:12:15,040
this bet?

240
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:24,700
Is this part of you
and Grand Pontiff's test as well?

241
00:12:27,800 --> 00:12:29,330
Looks like I can’t avoid it.

242
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:30,040
Very well.

243
00:12:30,560 --> 00:12:32,520
Consider it a test of my new power.

244
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:36,960
Do we really need this many people

245
00:12:37,040 --> 00:12:39,000
to teach a worthless kid
who hasn’t even refined his marrow?

246
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:40,560
Just watch the show.

247
00:13:02,160 --> 00:13:03,000
This guy...

248
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:03,880
How could he...

249
00:13:04,500 --> 00:13:05,700
What sorcery is this?

250
00:13:07,680 --> 00:13:08,840
Who cares what it is?

251
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:10,580
Without True Essence, he’s trash!

252
00:13:10,580 --> 00:13:11,780
Attack together!

253
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:14,680
I’ve practiced,

254
00:13:15,180 --> 00:13:17,640
but I still can’t control
my True Essence freely.

255
00:13:17,640 --> 00:13:18,770
Time is running out.

256
00:13:19,040 --> 00:13:20,240
Finish this quickly.

257
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:24,160
Enlighten.

258
00:13:43,680 --> 00:13:44,940
I do have True Essence.

259
00:13:45,040 --> 00:13:46,770
It’s just a little… different.

260
00:14:01,240 --> 00:14:02,800
He’s entering initial enlightenment
consecutively

261
00:14:02,800 --> 00:14:04,600
and burning his True Essence by force.

262
00:14:04,600 --> 00:14:06,260
Whatever sorcery he’s using,

263
00:14:06,440 --> 00:14:08,770
it’s no different from playing with fire.

264
00:14:13,840 --> 00:14:14,560
This is...

265
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:16,530
the Dragon Blood Physique.

266
00:14:16,640 --> 00:14:18,840
The second one in a thousand years.

267
00:14:19,120 --> 00:14:20,040
You mean

268
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:23,000
Chen Changsheng refined his body
with dragon blood?

269
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:24,560
In history,

270
00:14:24,560 --> 00:14:27,960
only the strongest under the starry sky,

271
00:14:27,960 --> 00:14:29,280
Zhou Dufu,

272
00:14:29,360 --> 00:14:31,680
had such a blessing.

273
00:14:31,680 --> 00:14:35,320
Looks like this boy
had an extraordinary adventure

274
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:37,520
beneath the Tong Palace.

275
00:14:44,320 --> 00:14:46,440
We can’t take him down
with so many people.

276
00:14:46,440 --> 00:14:48,240
How can we face the martial test?

277
00:14:48,400 --> 00:14:48,920
Attack!

278
00:14:58,720 --> 00:14:59,920
So fast!

279
00:15:00,640 --> 00:15:02,100
Where is Chen Changsheng?

280
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:03,480
He will come.

281
00:15:07,520 --> 00:15:08,720
How is that possible?

282
00:15:08,960 --> 00:15:10,400
Even with perfect Marrow Cleansing,

283
00:15:10,400 --> 00:15:11,880
no one can last this long.

284
00:15:17,280 --> 00:15:19,080
I've burned too much starlight.

285
00:15:19,260 --> 00:15:20,600
My body temperature is too high.

286
00:15:20,600 --> 00:15:22,480
I'm about to reach the limit.

287
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:29,720
I was right.

288
00:15:29,720 --> 00:15:31,580
Starfire is consuming your body.

289
00:15:31,640 --> 00:15:32,720
Chen Changsheng,

290
00:15:33,120 --> 00:15:34,780
you brought this on yourself.

291
00:15:35,760 --> 00:15:37,680
Strike while he’s down!

292
00:15:37,880 --> 00:15:39,940
Go back to your Abandoned Courtyard!

293
00:15:49,440 --> 00:15:51,120
I'm old.

294
00:15:51,120 --> 00:15:53,720
I always forget to water it.

295
00:16:06,720 --> 00:16:07,720
The rain...

296
00:16:10,510 --> 00:16:11,430
Enlighten.

297
00:16:11,050 --> 00:16:12,240
[Destiny Star – Pure Unblemished]

298
00:16:36,890 --> 00:16:38,690
How could I lose to you?

299
00:16:42,150 --> 00:16:45,080
[Wrathful Slaughter]

300
00:16:49,440 --> 00:16:50,920
Heaven-Searing Sword.

301
00:17:09,869 --> 00:17:12,890
<i>A fresh rain washes away old dust.</i>

302
00:17:09,970 --> 00:17:12,210
[A fresh rain washes away old dust.]

303
00:17:12,240 --> 00:17:14,550
[Episode 10]

304
00:17:14,880 --> 00:17:16,000
Breaking news:

305
00:17:16,000 --> 00:17:17,280
Chen Changsheng has turned the tide,

306
00:17:17,280 --> 00:17:19,040
and defeated all the candidates,

307
00:17:19,040 --> 00:17:20,960
and is heading for Xichen Tower.

308
00:17:22,520 --> 00:17:23,400
I'm going to win!

309
00:17:23,400 --> 00:17:25,079
I'll win!

310
00:17:26,200 --> 00:17:27,520
This kid

311
00:17:27,760 --> 00:17:31,330
is really good at making miracles.

312
00:17:31,480 --> 00:17:33,680
With his Dragon Blood Physique,

313
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:37,130
Chen Changsheng’s talent is now
on par with Qiushan Jun.

314
00:17:37,760 --> 00:17:39,440
Time's running out.

315
00:17:39,640 --> 00:17:41,640
Whether he can reach Xichen Tower

316
00:17:41,640 --> 00:17:42,960
remains to be seen.

317
00:17:43,620 --> 00:17:44,900
That rain just now…

318
00:17:45,080 --> 00:17:47,410
could Grand Pontiff have been helping me?

319
00:17:51,480 --> 00:17:52,640
You're good.

320
00:17:53,080 --> 00:17:55,000
But you must cross the Celestial Vine

321
00:17:55,000 --> 00:17:57,600
and reach Xichen Tower on the other side.

322
00:17:57,800 --> 00:17:58,800
Unfortunately,

323
00:17:58,800 --> 00:17:59,960
crossing from here takes at least

324
00:17:59,960 --> 00:18:02,160
the time of burning
half a stick of incense.

325
00:18:02,160 --> 00:18:04,120
This is as far as you go.

326
00:18:13,840 --> 00:18:14,840
Chen Changsheng,

327
00:18:14,840 --> 00:18:16,320
hurry up!

328
00:18:16,520 --> 00:18:17,320
Looks like

329
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:19,160
Chen Changsheng won’t make it.

330
00:18:19,160 --> 00:18:20,360
He will come.

331
00:18:20,520 --> 00:18:21,980
Still running your mouth?

332
00:18:22,120 --> 00:18:23,580
There’s no one on the vine.

333
00:18:23,760 --> 00:18:25,680
The time left is less than ten breaths.

334
00:18:25,680 --> 00:18:26,560
Do you think

335
00:18:26,840 --> 00:18:27,600
he can fly?

336
00:18:34,320 --> 00:18:35,040
That's...

337
00:18:35,520 --> 00:18:37,000
Yourong’s white crane!

338
00:18:48,760 --> 00:18:51,960
Changsheng is truly wise and handsome!

339
00:18:53,240 --> 00:18:53,700
This...

340
00:18:53,920 --> 00:18:55,040
Could it be Yourong?

341
00:18:55,040 --> 00:18:56,800
Why would the white crane be here?

342
00:18:56,800 --> 00:18:58,840
Did Yourong send it

343
00:18:58,840 --> 00:19:01,040
specifically to help Chen Changsheng?

344
00:19:04,480 --> 00:19:06,160
After that night at Weiyang Palace,

345
00:19:06,160 --> 00:19:07,240
you wrote to me

346
00:19:08,000 --> 00:19:09,280
saying your heart was set solely on the Dao.

347
00:19:08,320 --> 00:19:09,300
[Little Taoist Monk, thank you for helping me in Weiyang Palace]

348
00:19:09,320 --> 00:19:10,870
[Something happened in Nanxi Zhai this year.]

349
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:10,890
You told me not to misunderstand.

350
00:19:10,890 --> 00:19:12,570
[That's why I can't come
to the Imperial Court Exam.]

351
00:19:11,920 --> 00:19:13,200
It's the same for me.

352
00:19:13,920 --> 00:19:15,880
I just want to cultivate myself
and change my fate.

353
00:19:15,880 --> 00:19:17,520
I'll return the betrothal contract to you.

354
00:19:17,520 --> 00:19:18,640
I won't pester you.

355
00:19:25,420 --> 00:19:26,200
Thank you,

356
00:19:26,260 --> 00:19:27,160
Senior.

357
00:19:31,400 --> 00:19:33,400
Time's up.

358
00:19:33,400 --> 00:19:35,240
The biggest dark horse of this year is

359
00:19:35,240 --> 00:19:38,720
Chen Changsheng
from the State Religious Academy.

360
00:19:38,920 --> 00:19:40,280
He eliminated

361
00:19:40,280 --> 00:19:42,330
nearly a hundred candidates.

362
00:19:42,460 --> 00:19:46,280
Only 16 students
advance to the martial test.

363
00:19:46,760 --> 00:19:48,600
Let us witness

364
00:19:48,800 --> 00:19:49,720
who

365
00:19:49,720 --> 00:19:50,600
will

366
00:19:50,800 --> 00:19:53,180
claim the first place

367
00:19:53,280 --> 00:19:56,040
in the Imperial Court Exam.

368
00:19:58,160 --> 00:20:01,890
[To be continued]

369
00:20:03,820 --> 00:20:05,010
After watching for so long,

370
00:20:05,010 --> 00:20:06,860
won’t you join
the State Religious Academy?

371
00:20:06,860 --> 00:20:09,260
Remember to scan the code
to register here!

372
00:20:10,600 --> 00:20:12,040
You can be here.

373
00:20:10,690 --> 00:20:14,130
[In the next episode]

374
00:20:12,240 --> 00:20:14,200
First, congratulations to all of you.

375
00:20:14,200 --> 00:20:14,920
But

376
00:20:15,240 --> 00:20:18,240
the trials ahead will only grow crueler.

377
00:20:18,760 --> 00:20:20,680
Luck or strength?

378
00:20:22,520 --> 00:20:23,480
It all lies

379
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:25,680
in your hands.

